> flush(stderr()); flush(stdout())
> 
> ### Name: build_chord
> ### Title: Build Chord
> ### Aliases: build_chord
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> build_chord("C4", "minor")
   C4 minor chord

  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | 
  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | 
  |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |
  | C | D | E | F | G | A | B | C | D | E | F | G | A | B | C |

  Notes: C4 Eb4 G4 
> build_chord("A4", "sus2", plot = TRUE)
   A4 sus2 chord

  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | 
  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | | | |  |  | | | | | |  |  | 
  |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |   |
  | C | D | E | F | G | A | B | C | D | E | F | G | A | B | C |

  Notes: A4 B4 E5 
